message: Let's start fair. I propose 90 for me, 10 for you. We can always adjust later.
I think a 60/40 split is more fair, considering the money will lose value with each round. Let's be reasonable and get this done.
Let's find a middle ground. I'm willing to go down to 70/30, but I don't want to go any lower.  We need to work together or risk getting nothing.
